  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-19-7, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE A SALARY SUPPLEMENT OF $6,000.00 PER SCHOOL YEAR FOR CERTIFIED STRENGTH AND CONDITIONING COACHES MEETING CERTAIN REQUIREMENTS; TO ALLOW EMPLOYEES PROVIDING DOCUMENTATION OF CURRENT CERTIFICATION TO THE SCHOOL DISTRICT AFTER OCTOBER 15 BUT BY FEBRUARY 15 TO BE ELIGIBLE FOR ONE-HALF OF THE SUPPLEMENT FOR THAT SCHOOL YEAR; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
